events.name: 【146】出来心と下心 自動実行

parameters:
Thief Nora: T-The smell of beasts is incredible...! There
must be a beast lurking nearby!
Do you want to enter the boss area?
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Clea: I'll go ahead. If any beasts come out, please take
care of them.
Clea: Something is moving at high speed...
Thief Nora: Clea-san! Up here! They're jumping at us!
Clea: It seems impossible to take them down easily...

Clea: We managed to defeat them all... Let's report to our
client, Mr. Apros.

Mage Relm: Hey, no rain please! My precious grimoire will
get wet!

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, it seems like even the wine is
getting diluted.
Mage Relm: This is no time for jokes!

Thief Nora: With this heavy rain, our noses and ears won't
be of any use...

Clea: It's dangerous to move carelessly, but there's also a
possibility of being attacked by other beasts.

??? 'There's a hunter's cabin nearby! I'll lead the way, so
follow me!'
